Ramiel and Gogolan wanted to start the conference, but with only two 
representatives, it seemed useless. They made another call.

Gogolan: To all factions, we are the Angelions and wish to discuss 
with representatives of your groups. We demand that you come unarmed 
for security reasons. Please confirm your arrival.
